---
title: Chilli and Honey Glazed Pork Steak with Roasted Pepper, Couscous and Mint Yoghurt
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chilli and Honey Glazed Pork Steak in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
